  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the short story of Ryan, whose shortcut off a hiking path leads to a creepy church in the mountains. Find someone to get directions back home, solve puzzles to progress, collect items to survive, and get out alive. You may even want to find the hidden side story to learn the true past of the abandoned church. However, you choose to play, just know this is a single-level, short story game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
